</div><div class="field-item even"><div class="entity entity-paragraphs-item paragraphs-item-unesco-text " id="content--6729">
  <div class="content">

    
      <h3></h3>
      <h2>Second consolidated report</h2>
<p>The <a href="http://unesdoc.unesco.org/images/0021/002108/210804e.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>second consolidated report</strong></a> on the measures taken by UNESCO Member States for the implementation of the Recommendation concerning the Promotion and Use of Multilingualism and Universal Access to Cyberspace was examined by the Executive Board at its 186th session in Spring 2011 (Ref.: <a href="http://unesdoc.unesco.org/images/0019/001916/191614e.pdf" target="_blank">186 EX/19 Part IV</a>) and at the 36th session of the General Conference in Autumn 2011 (Ref.: <a href="http://unesdoc.unesco.org/images/0021/002108/210804e.pdf" target="_blank">36 C/26</a>).</p>
<p><strong>Member States’ reports</strong> submitted to UNESCO’s Secretariat for the preparation of the second consolidated report:</p>

    
  </div>
