</div><div class="field-item odd"><div class="entity entity-paragraphs-item paragraphs-item-unesco-text " id="content--6909">
  <div class="content">

    
      <h3></h3>
      <h2>Training of decision-makers in policy measures advised by the Recommendation</h2>
<p>In 2011, UNESCO provided assistance to Member States to train decision-makers in implementing the policy measures put forward by the recommendation. UNESCO carried out several training activities in the field of universal access to information and the promotion and use of multilingualism in partnership with the Organization of American States (OAS).</p>

    
  </div>
